snippet.title: AMBER'S 2015 SUBARU BRZ LIMITED REVIEW
snippet.description:
Today I got to review Amber's 2015 Subaru BRZ. This is a fun little car and I wouldn't mind driving it every day if I was in the market for something like this! Although, I think I prefer something with a LOT more horsepower ;) 
The S2000 is another great option that I forgot to mention, and I may just pick one up in the near future.

If you guys want to see more reviews, HIT THAT LIKE BUTTON, leave a comment below, & if you're new here; SUBSCRIBE so you can get all the notifications of my new uploads every day! :)

200HP at redline
6 speed manual gear box
